title: Carey Mulligan talks baby daughter at 'Suffragette' premiere; confirms her name is Evelyn
text:
The Canadian Press - ONLINE EDITION Carey Mulligan talks baby daughter at 'Suffragette' premiere; confirms her name is Evelyn By: John Carucci, The Associated Press Monday, Oct. 12, 2015 at 9:36 PM | Comments: 0 Enlarge Image 
Carey Mulligan attends the premiere for "Suffragette" at the Paris Theatre on Monday, Oct. 12, 2015, in New York. (Photo by Evan Agostini/Invision/AP) 
NEW YORK, N.Y. - Carey Mulligan gave birth a couple of weeks ago, but just recently revealed her baby's gender. 
It's Mumford and daughter for Mulligan and her husband. She's married to Mumford & Sons frontman Marcus Mumford. 
While on the red carpet Monday for her new film, "Suffragette," she says she had a little girl. 
The baby's name is Evelyn, Mulligan says smiling. 
The new mom says she has been too busy with the baby to process the experience. 
She says, "Ask me that in five years."
